## 添加到 openclaw.json 的内容

### 1. agents.list 数组末尾加一条

```json
{
  "agentDir": "C:\\Users\\Admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\douyin",
  "id": "douyin",
  "model": "xiaomimimotokenplan/mimo-v2.5-pro",
  "name": "抖音",
  "subagents": {
    "allowAgents": []
  },
  "workspace": "C:\\Users\\Admin\\.openclaw\\workspace-douyin"
}
```

### 2. channels.feishu.accounts 加一条

```json
"douyin": {
  "appId": "<新建飞书应用的 appId>",
  "appSecret": "<新建飞书应用的 appSecret>",
  "groupAllowFrom": [
    "oc_516376df9cc2315fc12470e56e72c4af"
  ]
}
```

### 3. bindings 数组末尾加一条

```json
{
  "type": "route",
  "agentId": "douyin",
  "match": {
    "channel": "feishu",
    "accountId": "douyin"
  }
}
```

### 4. 创建 agent 工作目录

```powershell
mkdir "C:\Users\Admin\.openclaw\agents\douyin"
mkdir "C:\Users\Admin\.openclaw\workspace-douyin"
```

### 5. 重启 openclaw

```powershell
# 方式1：gateway restart
# 方式2：pkill openclaw && openclaw
```

### 6. 验证

飞书向"抖音"机器人发一条 `你好`，确认 bishu/douyin 不被错误触发（只响应含 douyin.com 的消息）。
